lead_paragraph: The release of the two women from the Czech Republic, who were kidnapped from a bus in Pakistan by gunmen, was negotiated by a Turkish humanitarian organization.

headline.main: 2 Czech Tourists Abducted in 2013 Have Been Freed in Pakistan
